  Locus:
    Page: 214
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Grief
---
No one is so bereaved, so miserable, that he cannot find someone else to
succor, someone who needs friendship, understanding and courage more than
he. The unselfish effort to bring cheer to others will be the beginning of
a happier life for ourselves.
